---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Structured Data Cabling & Fibre Splicing Hamilton"
  description="Professional network infrastructure, 10GbE copper and fibre optic installations. Site Safe certified data cabling experts for Hamilton and Waikato businesses."
>
  <div class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-tag">Services — Networking & Data</span>
      <h1 class="page-title">Networking &amp;<br /><em>Data Cabling</em></h1>
      <p class="page-sub">Structured cabling, fibre optics and 10GbE installations built to last.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-grid">
        <div class="prose">
          <h2>Infrastructure Built the Right Way</h2>
          <p>
            Whether you're running cable for a new commercial build, upgrading to 10 Gigabit Ethernet,
            or extending your CCTV system, Central Communications has the skills and qualifications
            to get it done — on time, and to spec.
          </p>
          <p>
            We are certified for at-heights work, elevated work platforms, and hold Site Safe accreditation.
            It is quite likely we've already tackled the specific cabling challenge you're facing.
          </p>

          <h2>10 Gigabit Ethernet</h2>
          <p>
            10 Gigabit Ethernet (10GbE) is here, and it makes your network rocket. We're experts in
            fibre splicing and copper structured data cabling. Be it cabling for your CCTV system,
            phone system, or general network — we've got the cabling solution for you.
          </p>
          <p>
            Our 10GbE installations typically combine SFP+ fibre uplinks for inter-cabinet connections
            with Cat6 copper for desktop/device distribution — giving you the best performance at every
            point in the network.
          </p>

          <h2>Our Networking Brands</h2>
          <div class="brands-grid">
            <img src="/assets/images/mikrotik.svg"  alt="MikroTik" width="120" height="40" />
            <img src="/assets/images/unifi.svg"     alt="Unifi"    width="120" height="40" />
            <img src="/assets/images/grandstream.svg" alt="Grandstream" width="120" height="40" />
            <img src="/assets/images/legrand.svg"   alt="Legrand"  width="120" height="40" />
          </div>

          <h2>What's included?</h2>
          <ul class="feature-list">
            <li>Structured Cat5e / Cat6 / Cat6A copper cabling</li>
            <li>Fibre optic installation and splicing</li>
            <li>10 Gigabit Ethernet (10GbE) infrastructure</li>
            <li>Patch panel &amp; cabinet installation</li>
            <li>Commercial builds — at-heights &amp; Site Safe certified</li>
            <li>CCTV and phone system cabling</li>
            <li>Cable testing &amp; certification</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="sidebar">
          <div class="cta-box">
            <h3>Planning a cabling project?</h3>
            <p>We'd love to hear about your project. Call us or send a message for a quote.</p>
            <a href="tel:+6480084800038" class="btn btn-ember">0800 848 0038</a>
            <a href="/#contact" class="btn btn-outline" style="margin-top:0.75rem;">Send a message</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-title { font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem); color: #e8f1ff; margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem; }
  .page-title em { font-style: normal; color: #0ea5e9; }
  .page-sub { font-size: 1.1rem; color: #7ea3c8; max-width: 520px; }
  .content-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 340px; gap: 4rem; align-items: start; }
  .brands-grid { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 2rem; align-items: center; margin: 1.5rem 0; }
  .brands-grid img { height: 32px; width: auto; filter: brightness(0) invert(0.6); transition: filter 0.2s; }
  .brands-grid img:hover { filter: none; }
  .feature-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.6rem; }
  .feature-list li { padding-left: 1.5rem; position: relative; color: #1e3a5f; font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.6; }
  .feature-list li::before { content: ''; position: absolute; left: 0; top: 0.6rem; width: 6px; height: 6px; background: #0ea5e9; border-radius: 50%; }
  .sidebar { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.5rem; position: sticky; top: 6rem; }
  .cta-box { background: #0c1d35; border: 1px solid rgba(14,165,233,0.15); border-radius: 1rem; padding: 1.75rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem; }
  .cta-box h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; color: #e8f1ff; margin: 0; }
  .cta-box p { font-size: 0.875rem; color: #7ea3c8; margin: 0; line-height: 1.6; }
  .cta-box .btn-outline { color: #e8f1ff; border-color: rgba(232, 241, 255, 0.35); }
  .cta-box .btn-outline:hover { color: #38bdf8; border-color: #38bdf8; }
  @media (max-width: 900px) { .content-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .sidebar { position: static; } }
</style>
